# ===============================================
# Global .dockerignore for Monorepo (project_root/.dockerignore)
# ===============================================

# --- General Development/OS Files ---
.git
.github
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
*.swp
.venv
.env
*.log

# --- Python Artifacts ---
# Virtual environment directories
**/venv
# Bytecode and build artifacts
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
**/*.egg-info
**/build

# --- Node/Frontend Artifacts (CRITICAL TO EXCLUDE) ---
# Node dependency folders
**/node_modules
# Vite/Webpack/Build output folders
**/dist
**/build
**/out

# --- Alembic/DB Specific Files ---
# Alembic generates files inside the migrations directory, which should 
# be copied as source code, but exclude internal artifacts if any.
# Typically, Alembic directories are kept.